One real-world application that can be built using Salesforce is a Hospital Management System.
This application can help hospitals manage:
Patient records
Doctor appointments
Billing details
Medicine information
Customer support services
For example, when a patient visits the hospital, all their details and medical history can be stored safely in Salesforce. Doctors and staff can quickly access the information, schedule appointments, and provide better service.
In simple words, Salesforce helps hospitals work faster, stay organized, and improve patient care.
